{% set page = "occasions" %}
{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block main %}

    <section class="intro">
        <div class="intro-text">
            <p>Whatever the occasion, I can design and make your celebration cake, be it for a birthday, wedding, anniversary, corporate event, christening, baby shower, Easter, Christmas...etc.</p>

            <p>If you have a design in mind, that's great, or you can choose a cake from my portfolio or let me design the cake for you.</p>

            <p>Cakes can be finished in either buttercream or fondant and you can choose from an extensive list of <a href="/flavours">sponge flavours</a>. I can also cater for certain dietary requirements like dairy and gluten free.</p>

            <p>Decorative choices include chocolate or coloured drips, fondant or real flowers, fondant models, airbrushing, edible images and balloons.</p>
        
            <div class="cta">
                <h3>Ready to make your occasion special?</h3>
                <a
                    class="button"
                    href="/#contact"
                >
                    Contact me
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

